I'm upset that you're upset
All I want is for you to be happy
And that's why I have to set you free
Engine will usually put you into a position to win, or win outright. I think cards like that are fine. That being said, I understand-
Am I being threatened?
Or is this a promise?
PE can win but the turns take forever.
And it’s a lot of “sit and watch me play Magic, noob”
